rc=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Scaled_Chest.png?426283\" width=\"64\" height=\"65\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Scaled_Chest\" title=\"Scaled Chest\">Scaled Chest</a><br><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" title=\"Reign of Giants\"><img alt=\"Reign of Giants icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Reign_of_Giants_icon.png/20px-Reign_of_Giants_icon.png?12c8d5\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\"></a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Spider_Eggs\" title=\"Spider Eggs\"><img alt=\"Spider Eggs\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Spider_Eggs.png?2102a4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Spider_Eggs\" title=\"Spider Eggs\">Spider Eggs</a><br><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" title=\"Reign of Giants\"><img alt=\"Reign of Giants icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Reign_of_Giants_icon.png/20px-Reign_of_Giants_icon.png?12c8d5\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Webber\" title=\"Webber\"><img alt=\"Webber Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Webber_Portrait.png/20px-Webber_Portrait.png?dd96ec\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sea_Chest\" title=\"Sea Chest\"><img alt=\"Sea Chest\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Sea_Chest.png?2e4eff\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sea_Chest\" title=\"Sea Chest\">Sea Chest</a><br><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/20px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\"></a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Limestone_Wall\" title=\"Limestone Wall\"><img alt=\"Limestone Wall\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Limestone_Wall.png?8552b8\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Limestone Wall</a><br><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/20px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\"></a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wall\" title=\"Sea Wall\"><img alt=\"Sea Wall\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Sea_Wall.png?97ce46\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Sea Wall</a><br><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/20px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\"></a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wildbore_House\" title=\"Wildbore House\"><img alt=\"Wildbore House\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Wildbore_House.png?7c055e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wildbore_House\" title=\"Wildbore House\">Wildbore House</a><br><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon