  "title": "Structures Tab",
  "wikitext": "{{Exclusivity|Don't Starve|Reign of Giants|Shipwrecked|Hamlet}}\n{{for|the filter in [[Don't Starve Together]]|Decorations Filter|Structures Filter}}\n[[File:Icon Structures.png|right|thumb|Tab Icon]]\n{{Quote|OCCUPIED|WX-78}}\n'''Structures''' are objects which can be built using resources found throughout the world. Most of them must be prototyped using a [[Science Machine]] or [[Alchemy Engine]] the first time they are built. This will consume the necessary resources even if the structure placement is cancelled (RMB), however placing can be done at any later time without additional costs by re-selecting the structure in [[Game Tabs|Crafting Tabs]]. Structures can be destroyed with a [[Hammer]] or a [[Deconstruction Staff]]  to receive at least 50% or 100% of the resources used to build them respectively (except [[Walls]], [[Wooden Flooring]], and [[Sign]]s which give 1 [[item]] only).\n\nSome structures can be naturally spawned in the world, such as [[Pig House]]s and [[Stone Wall]]s surrounding the [[Box Thing]]. In fact, many unique [[Set Pieces]] made from multiple structures can be randomly generated at world creation.\n\n==[[File:Gift Icon.png|32px]] Downloadable Content==\nIn the ''[[Reign of Giants]]'' DLC, the player can craft [[Scaled Chest]]s and while playing as [[Webber]], [[Spider Eggs]] in the Structures Tab.\n\nIn the ''[[Shipwrecked]]'' DLC, [[Sea Chest]]s, [[Wall|Limestone Walls]], [[Wall|Sea Walls]], [[Ballphin Palace]]s, [[Wildbore House]]s, [[Prime Ape Hut]]s, [[Dragoon Den]]s, [[Snakeskin Rug]]s, [[Sandbag]]s, and [[Sand Castle]]s were added to this tab.\n\nThe ''[[Don't Starve: Hamlet|Hamlet]]'' DLC introduces [[Cork Barrel]]s, [[Beard Hair Rug]], [[Lawn Turf]], [[Cultivated Turf]] and [[Dense Turf]] to the Structures Tab.\n\n\n==Craftable Items and Structures==\nThe following items and structures can be crafted in the Structures Tab:\n\n<div style=\"clear:both; font-weight: bold\"><gallery columns=\"6\" position=\"center\" widths=\"64\" captionalign=\"center\" captionsize=\"medium\" bordersize=\"none\" spacing=\"medium\" hideaddbutton=\"true\" navigation=\"true\">\n\nChest.png|link=Chest|[[Chest]]\nSign.png|link=Sign|[[Sign]]\nMini Sign.png|link=Mini Sign|[[Mini Sign]]\nWood Fence.png|link=Wood Fence|[[Wood Fence]]\nWood Gate.png|link=Wood Gate|[[Wood Gate]]\nHay Wall.png|link=Hay Wall|[[Wall|Hay Wall]]\nWood Wall.png|link=Wood Wall|[[Wall|Wood Wall]]\nStone Wall.png|link=Stone Wall|[[Wall|Stone Wall]]\nPig House.png|link=Pig House|[[Pig House]]\nRabbit Hutch.png|link=Rabbit Hutch|[[Rabbit Hutch]]\nBirdcage.png|link=Birdcage|[[Birdcage]]\nCobblestones.png|link=Cobblestones|[[Cobblestones]]\nWooden Flooring.png|link=Wooden Flooring|[[Wooden Flooring]]\nCheckerboard Flooring.png|link=Checkerboard Flooring|[[Checkerboard Flooring]]\nCarpeted Flooring.png|link=Carpeted Flooring|[[Carpeted Flooring]]\nPotted Fern.png|link=Potted Fern|[[Potted Fern]]\nScaled Chest.png|link=Scaled Chest|[[Scaled Chest]]<br>{{Pic|20|Reign of Giants icon|Reign of Giants}}\nSpider Eggs.png|link=Spider Eggs|[[Spider Eggs]]<br>{{Pic|20|Reign of Giants icon|Reign of Giants}}{{Pic|20|Webber Portrait|Webber}}\nSea Chest.png|link=Sea Chest|[[Sea Chest]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nLimestone Wall.png|link=Limestone Wall|[[Wall|Limestone Wall]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nSea Wall.png|link=Wall|[[Wall|Sea Wall]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nWildbore House.png|link=Wildbore House|[[Wildbore House]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nPrime Ape Hut.png|link=Prime Ape Hut|[[Prime Ape Hut]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nBallphin Palace.png|link=Ballphin Palace|[[Ballphin Palace]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nDragoon Den.png|link=Dragoon Den|[[Dragoon Den]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nSnakeskin Rug.png|link=Snakeskin Rug|[[Snakeskin Rug]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nSand Bag.png|link=Sandbag|[[Sandbag]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nSand Castle.png|link=Sand Castle|[[Sand Castle]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nCork Barrel.png|link=Cork Barrel|[[Cork Barrel]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}\nBeard Hair Rug.png|link=Beard Hair Rug|[[Beard Hair Rug]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}\nLawn Turf.png|link=Lawn Turf|[[Lawn Turf]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}\nCultivated Turf.png|link=Cultivated Turf|[[Cultivated Turf]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}\nDense Turf.png|link=Dense Turf|[[Dense Turf]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}\n</gallery></div>\n\n{{Tabs}}\n[[ru:Конструкции]]\n[[vi:Thẻ Kiến Trúc]]\n[[ko:구조물 탭]]\n__NOTOC__"
